07/01/2021
meshmsg by Retrospect Security
Connect to a meshtastic radio over usb and communicate using a bash interface.

Scripts:
receive.sh - receive lora messages and open the chat window
status.sh - show status window of local nodes
send.sh - sending lora messages to all users
screen_rc - config to create proper screen

